        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-2">Azure Deployment Configuration</h3>
  <p class="text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-4">Azure does not support listing deployments via the Data Plane API. You must configure deployment names manually. During model discovery, Model Prism automatically detects which deployments use the Chat Completions API and which use the newer Responses API (e.g. gpt-5.3-codex). See the Azure REST API specs for details.</p>

