  <h2 id="authentication-methods" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Authentication Methods</h2>
  <p class="text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-4">Different provider types use different authentication mechanisms:</p>
  <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
    <table class="w-full border-collapse">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="bg-white/5 text-left text-white/70 px-4 py-2 text-sm">Method</th>
          <th class="bg-white/5 text-left text-white/70 px-4 py-2 text-sm">Provider Types</th>
          <th class="bg-white/5 text-left text-white/70 px-4 py-2 text-sm">Details</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td class="border-t border-white/10 px-4 py-2 text-white/50 text-sm">API Key</td>
          <td class="border-t border-white/10 px-4 py-2 text-white/50 text-sm"><code class="bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[#38bdf8] text-sm font-mono">openai</code>, <code class="bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[#38bdf8] text-sm font-mono">azure</code>, <code class="bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[#38bdf8] text-sm font-mono">openrouter</code></td>
